Personality

08 May 2019

After reading this article today I was reminded Lobsterboy’s personality test last year, but I don’t think I ever wrote about the results. The self reported test measures the ‘Big Five’ personality taits, each of which are split into two sub-traits. All numbers relate to percentiles.

  • Agreeableness - 57
    • Compassion - 48
    • Politness - 65
  • Conscientiousness - 0
